cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DS

The paper discusses the use of data mining techniques in managing and analyzing large volumes of data generated by multinational companies and organizations. This falls under the category of database systems (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as data mining involves machine learning algorithms. The paper also mentions the effectiveness of managerial decision-making, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and the use of data to make strategic decisions. Finally, the paper discusses the transformation of various fields through data mining, which is related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
